$interpreted: Bear Scout: Chieftain, illegal miners are in Totemtaff again! They're heading west!
Dagger: Damn humans! Time to teach them a lesson!
Crushfang: Dagger, wait here.
Dagger: Let me come with you! Humans are easy targets!
Crushfang: Hmph! This isn't child's play! You could get yourself killed!
Dagger: I'm no—
Crushfang: Enough. You're staying here.
Teenage Bear: Come on! Get him!
Dagger: Found illegal miners out west! Who wants to come kick some human butt!?

Furygrowl: Can we do that...?
Alright, count me in!
Teenage Bear: Me too!
Bear Soldier: Let's get 'em outta here!
Dagger: Dinner's served, boys!
Dagger: Pfft~ Nothin' to it!
Furygrowl: The chieftain is here.
Furygrowl: Grrouu~ Grrouu.
Bear Soldier: Grrouu~ Grrouu.

Crushfang: Didn't I tell you to wait in the cave?
You disobey me!?

Dagger: I got the humans, didn't I?
They woulda been long gone if we had to wait for you slowpokes!
Crushfang: Don't underestimate the humans! They're full of tricks. I owe it to your father to keep you safe...
Dagger: That is none of your concern! I'm not a cub anymore!
